In the blog [_Gatos Frentudos
[es]_](http://gatosfrentudos.blogspot.com/2010/08/sin-empleo-sin-seguridad-y-
sin.html)Chambita Hernandez writes about a recent decision to ban cheerleaders
from independence celebrations, starting with the bicentennial. Since 1960,
cheerleaders have been part of annual independence parades.

